SELECT current_year, current_month, current_day, game_id, termination_id,
  losing_player_id, moves_until_termination, terminated_by_player_id,
  termination_comment, termination_timestamp, termination_type, winning_player_id
  FROM cs2_keyspace_5.cs2_game_termination
  WHERE termination_type = 'Manual'
  ALLOW FILTERING;
